name: De Ammon #004 : To the future
description:
De Ammon traveled to the future, when he got there he found a difference in the use of colors, of course he was amazed by the contrasting and sparkling colors.
at night he has to wear a gas mask because he is not used to the smells around him, what's more, everyone wears it at this time, and what makes De Ammon the most uncomfortable is when he walks outside there are several orbs monitoring his movements. What should De Ammon do with these orbs?
